<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="the-former-the-latter">the former ... the latter</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>前者…后者：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>John and James are brothers. The former is a teacher; the latter is an engineer. 
约翰和詹姆斯是兄弟，前者是老师，后者是工程师。</p></div></div>